com.artisan.services

Interface ArtisanBoundActivity

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArtisanActivity, ArtisanFragmentActivity

    public interface ArtisanBoundActivity
    This is an interface for Activities which are bound to the Artisan Service. This means that Artisan can provide analytics and add experiments, optimizations, personalizations for this Activity. All of your app's Activities should be ArtisanBoundActivities either by extending ArtisanActivity or by explicitly implementing this interface.
